      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained, making it perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend trips. It runs great and looks even better in person! I've truly loved driving this beauty, and I\u2019m sure you will too. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
