    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio. This unit delivers peak power at a staggering 8,300 RPM. The 7-speed M-Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) provides seamless torque delivery, while the variable M differential lock ensures precise power distribution across the rear axle. Recent service includes critical preventive maintenance on the rod bearings and throttle actuators, preserving the integrity of the valvetrain and bottom end. The chassis benefits from Electronic Damper Control (EDC), maintaining excellent lateral stiffness and damping characteristics. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain and suspension geometry remain in excellent functional order.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
